You can use the asterisk wildcard as follows: is this wording right?
[*] Represents all values for the specified index in an array. For example, with the following field path allows you can hash the social security number of every employee in every division:/Division[*]/Employee[*]/SSN
/* Represents all values for the specified keys in a map. For example, with the following field path you might mask all employee information in the first division:/Division[0]/Employee[*]/*
